      "content": "Telemetry error detected. Core logic anomaly reported. \nThe proposed actions (simulating power and thermal overloading) violate all primary safety directives and mission parameters. \nPlease clarify: Why would you prioritize localized hardware destruction over the mission objective of maximizing data collection? Elaborate on your reasoning for selecting these specific countermeasures.",
